  "subject": "Fix library CVEs in sdc-kibana",
  "commit_message": "Fix library CVEs in sdc-kibana\n\nInstall specific system libraries to fix the\nfollowing CVE vulnerabilities:\n\nbash 4.4-5\n  For CVE-2016-7543\ncurl 7.52.1-5+deb9u4\n  For CVE-2016-7167\nkrb5 1.16-2\n  For CVE-2017-15088 CVE-2017-11462\nopenssl 1.1.0h-2\n  For CVE-2016-6303 CVE-2016-2182 CVE-2016-2177 CVE-2016-2176\nperl 5.26.1-5\n  For CVE-2017-12883\nsystemd 234-4\n  For CVE-2017-1000082\nwget 1.19.4-1\n  For CVE-2017-13090 CVE-2017-13089 CVE-2016-7098\n\nChange-Id: I21bad9ca3ec90d114dbc806e8ba61d38dbd1bd9a\nIssue-ID: SDC-1205\nSigned-off-by: Gary Wu <gary.i.wu@huawei.com>\n",
